      chapterActivity: 'A monthly market walk — a morning at the Union Square Greenmarket with a clipboard, tracking what the price of the same tomato does between 8 a.m. and closing, and what happens when rain breaks out at 10. Once a quarter, a field trip to the NYSE visitor gallery or to the NY Fed, and an evening over beers arguing about whether the data match the textbook.',

